Patch Set 1:

> (1 comment)
 > 
 > I have a nit about the commit message; otherwise this looks good.
 > 
 > Am I correct that image sharing will fail with an UnknownScheme
 > error until all old images have been lazy updated?  If so, we need
 > to make sure it shows up in the "Known Issues" of the multistore
 > release note.

Adding member to image will first retrieve the image using get call. So if metadata does not have associated store then it will be added to that image location.
